import React from "react"
import {LoginContainer,LoginHeader,LoginItem,LoginLabel,LoginInput,LoginBtn} from "./styles/loginstyle"
const Login = () =>{
    return(
        <LoginContainer>
            <LoginHeader>Login</LoginHeader>
            <LoginItem>
            <LoginLabel>Email</LoginLabel>
            <LoginInput type = "email" placeholder = "Enter your email" />
            </LoginItem>
            <LoginItem>
            <LoginLabel>Password</LoginLabel>
            <LoginInput type = "password" placeholder = "Enter your password" />
            </LoginItem>
            <LoginBtn>Login</LoginBtn>
        </LoginContainer>
    )
}
export default Login
